    "These investigations reveal a nuanced performance landscape where ChatGPT's effectiveness varies significantly based on the nature of the task.",
    "This discrepancy highlights a critical need for a deeper analysis of the reasoning capabilities of GAI to fully grasp its applicability and limitations in educational settings.",
    "Further inquiry into ChatGPT's application in chemistry education uncovers its mixed efficacy.",
    "For instance, although ChatGPT struggles to accurately perform chemical analysis or stoichiometry (Humphry & Fuller, 2023), it has also been shown to be useful in generating coherent lab reports (Emenike & Emenike, 2023).",
